snippet: WINSLOW--Eunice J.,of Locust Valley, NY on February 2, 2016. Wife of the late Scudder. Mother of Rolla Bruce Campbell, Eunice Graham Strigaro, the late Alison Fraser Swain and Cynthia Coit Waters. Sister of Priscilla Johnson McMillan, the late Stuart Holmes Johnson Jr. and Frank Coit Johnson II. Grandmother of April, Brooke, Caroline, Elisabeth, Allison, Stephen, Madeline, Randall, William and Timothy. Great-grandmother of five. Service at St. John's of Lattingtown, Tuesday, February 9th at 11am. Interment private. DodgeThomas.com. 1/3
